data.title: Siebel Integration Document
data.meta_description: Siebel Integration Document - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Oracle acquired BigMachines to offer two Configure, Price, and Quote (CPQ) cloud products: CPQ for Mid-Market and CPQ Platform. The products automate quoting, pricing, and sales workflows to help companies grow revenue. Partners can refer deals to earn fees, co-sell and implement solutions, or integrate their applications. Resources for partners are available on the Oracle CPQ Cloud Knowledge Zone to help them market the products.
